author: Google
description:
Want a custom 3D glass graphic wrapped in holiday lights? This two-step process uses Nano Banana and Veo 3.1:

1️⃣ Create: Open the Google app, press Lens, tap the 🍌, add your image, and ask it to: “transform the [image] into a 3d glass gradient wrapped with christmas lights, set against a dark gradient blue background.”

2️⃣ Animate: Pro/Ultra users, upload the new image to Gemini, select “Create videos (Veo 3.1),” and add the prompt: “the camera pushes backward and the [image] spins to its original position and stops after a full 360 degrees.” 

#GoogleGemini #Veo
title: Give your graphics a glow-up with Search ✨
